{"tid":1263663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋失物]急！係地鐵唔見咗passport！！","createTime":"2019-06-28T09:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T05:16:03.000Z","uid":270834,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f30cbb96c5e1780e574fe7d77c5d0bd225ac0a6","tid":1263663,"uid":270834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"係荃灣往中環方向嘅地鐵唔見咗passport <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經即時搵咗站職員同報咗警，但暫時未有發現，所以就上嚟問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間係大約4:50-5:00左右，<br />\n當時架車去到太子站，<br />\n袋仔入面裝住一本passport 同幾張證件相，<br />\n個袋係個好薄嘅白色防水磨沙膠面、有啲碎花同雀仔圖案。<br />\n本passport 係用嚟整留學visa，要補領要24日，好可能會趕唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求好心人執到然後見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa123b2655911871184e60464846370e2f8810a","tid":1263663,"uid":270834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e2e450341c7131043c440c1bc871b78cd46aac2","tid":1263663,"uid":270834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"有薄酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837cf7d030d69ab90ce5875e9333a25ee86207d7","tid":1263663,"uid":270834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91179f7a8f8df6c99c9218d15ae2763183901330","tid":1263663,"uid":270834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor